5. Track & Trace Table

Table: DPW_EXTERNAL_TRACK_AND_TRACE


---

Purpose

This table stores integration tracking data.


---

Key Fields

Field	Description

EVENT_ID	Linked event
REQUEST_ID	Linked request
EB_CUS_FLAG	Customer eligibility
EB_CUS_ID	Customer ID
EB_BAN_ID	Bank ID
